    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been maintained to the most exacting standards. Every surface and mechanical component reflects a level of care that transcends the standard used-car market. For the discerning collector or enthusiast seeking a definitive example of this model, this offering represents an investment-grade opportunity. Meticulously preserved and ready for immediate acquisition.",
