    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and meticulously maintained. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for all your upcoming adventures, you\u2019ve found it. Drop me a message if you want to come see it in person!",
