      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E39 M5 represents the pinnacle of the analog driving era. Powered by the S62 4.9L V8 featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, the powerplant delivers a linear torque curve and immediate throttle response. Mated to a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a factory 25% lock limited-slip differential, the drivetrain remains tight with crisp gear synchronization. The chassis retains its structural integrity, exhibiting zero subframe fatigue or oxidation. Every bushing and suspension component is within factory tolerances, maintaining the precise damping characteristics of the original Sachs valving. This example is mechanically synchronized and cosmetically immaculate, offering a pure, unadulterated longitudinal driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
