    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and shielded from the elements since day one. The exterior paintwork is flawless, possessing a deep, glass-like clarity with absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or scratches. The factory alloy wheels are pristine, wrapped in high-performance tires with nearly full tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, devoid of any creasing or wear, and still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every technological feature, sensor, and button functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service portfolio documented exclusively by authorized specialists. The engine bay is detailed to a high standard, showing no signs of age or use. This is not merely a used car; it is a collector-grade specimen that offers a 'new' driving experience for the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
