    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and high-pressure VANOS. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock, ensuring precise power delivery. Mechanically, this example is beyond reproach: the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced to ensure long-term reliability. The chassis maintains its factory-spec 50/50 weight distribution, offering telepathic handling. Finished in flawless Carbon Black over an untouched Nappa leather interior, this collector-grade specimen shows no signs of wear, retaining its original factory luster and mechanical tightness.",
